# Yohani De Silva — Frontend Developer Portfolio

This is my personal developer portfolio website.  
It showcases my projects, technical skills, and contact information.

The goal of this portfolio is to present my work as a frontend-focused developer and demonstrate my ability to build responsive, structured, and user-friendly web interfaces and desktop applications.

## 🌐 Live Website

https://ysdesilva21.github.io/personal-portfolio/

## 🚀 Features

- Responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile
- Clean UI with modern layout
- CSS variables for scalable styling
- Structured component-based sections
- Project showcase cards
- Skills and education section
- Contact and social media integration
- Mobile navigation menu

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Responsive Web Design
- Git & GitHub

